import 'slick-carousel';
 
class CarouselProduct {
	constructor($el) {
		const selectors = {
			carouselWrap: '.js-o-carousel-product__wrap',
		};
 
		const slickOptions = {
			fade: false,
			initialSlide: 0,
			infinite: true,
			dots: true,
			slide: '.js-o-carousel-product__item',
			dotsClass: 'o-carousel-product__dots',
			slidesToShow: 4,
			slidesToScroll: 1,
			mobileFirst: true,
			focusOnSelect: true,
			lazyLoad: 'ondemand',
			prevArrow: '.js-o-carousel-product__arrow--prev',
			nextArrow: '.js-o-carousel-product__arrow--next',
			zIndex: 0,
		};
 
		// Init Slick Carousel
		$el.find(selectors.carouselWrap).slick(slickOptions);
	}
}
 
export default CarouselProduct;
